title: DPS-BEST OF- Sep 16, 2020

description:
On Today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, Big Ten football announced its return today. Will we see all schools participate? ESPN's Kirk Herbstriet, LA Times Dan Woike and Hofer Reggie Miller all join the show. Plus, who's to blame for the Clippers bowing out in the 2nd round of the playoffs?
